          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Cowork is Claude's agentic desktop feature that manipulates local files, creates documents, and organizes your workspace, without writing code. Think of it as Claude Code for knowledge workers: same AI model, different interface designed for non-developers."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What can Cowork NOT do?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
