        "name": "When should I use Chat vs Cowork?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Chat (80%): reasoning, writing, coding, exploratory tasks. Cowork (20%): batch file operations, document creation, browser automation. Together they enable workflows impossible with either alone."
